<italic>p</italic>=0.03,
<xref ref-type="fig" rid="F1">Fig. 1</xref>), but not when compared with metastases (Q2TIPS: <italic>p</italic>=0.9, ITS-FAIR:
<italic>p</italic>=0.7) and meningiomas (Q2TIPS:
